title: Do yourselves a favour
body:
And watch some funny Korean Casting moments, one of my new favourite funny youtube video types ever.

EDIT: Here's a link to the best one in my opinion, thanks Maraudaur :P

https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=dyTEnb5GiRo - Korean Casters WORLDS 2015

Actually, all my laughter came from those videos you just posted, I just didn't wanna give everyone a clusterfuck of videos so I looked for a single video made up of all of them xD
Not what I expected, but gladly.
